-- Tottenham Tagets Mourinho Should Redknapp Leave, Mirror Reports
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-03-17T14:43:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-17/tottenham-tagets-mourinho-should-redknapp-leave-mirror-reports.html
Tottenham will look to hire  Jose Mourinho  should Harry Redknapp take the job as England national
team manager, the Daily Mirror said.  Spurs Chairman  Daniel Levy  has said he doesn’t want to lose
Redknapp, but has Mourinho as his main target if he does, the
Mirror said.  Mourinho is set to leave Real Madrid at the end of the
season and has stated a desire to return to the Premier League.
He’s also been linked with former club Chelsea after the Blues
fired Andre Villas-Boas on March 5.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
